$interpreted: Sanchez: Piece of trash, who told you to run around!?
Rune: San...chez...said...wait...here...
Sanchez: NINCOMPOOP! If only the prayer ceremony hadn't taken away all the good slaves...
Sanchez: ...Whatever. Everything the master wanted has basically been purchased.
Sanchez: Hey trash, we're leaving!
Rune: ...Noise...
Sanchez: IDIOT! The market's crowded. Of course there's noise. Get your act together, and quit screwing around!
Rune: It's...coming...from...there...
Sophie: Thank you! A big thanks to all of you!
Sophie: (Not even a smile. Well, I grew up in the circus. I'll show you what 'professional' means!)
Sophie: 100% natural! Guaranteed! The legendary, giant-horned demihuman deer——Hutchinson!!
Sophie: The porkiest, the prickliest hedgehog of them all——the amazing, precious prick, Hanbei!
Sophie: Last but certainly not least, the star of the show, the hotshot——Ru-yi!!
Sophie: As long as there's a smile, there's hope! Putting a smile on everyone's faces, Morgan's Marvelous Circus!
Sophie: I'm your Ringmaster, Sophie! Thanks for coming to the show! The cost of entrance - - just a smile. Come on now, pay up!
Rune: ...Smile...?
Sophie: Yes, just like that! Raise that mouth up just a little more!
Sanchez: Rune! You're looking for trouble, boy!
Sophie: Hey, he didn't hit you back!
Sophie: Here at Morgan's the audience's safety is always number one!
Sanchez: You...CLOWNS! Do you know who I am? I'm the servant of a Priest!
Ru-yi: So...Sophie, something's not right...
